text: Rhembastus laticollis is a species of leaf beetle of the Democratic Republic of the Congo. It was first described by the Belgian entomologist in 1942, from specimens collected by Gaston-François de Witte from the Albert National Park between 1933 and 1935. ==References== Category:Eumolpinae Category:Beetles of the Democratic Republic of the Congo Category:Beetles described in 1942
title: Rhembastus laticollis
